snippet.textDisplay:
Fareed and Ayaz were trained by their father The legendary Munshi Raziuddin, who in turn was the cousin of Bahauddin Qawwal.
Qawwali has its root from India when Amir Khusru wrote Qawwali for his teacher Sheikh Nizam Uddin Auliya some 800 hundred years ago . 
Boundaries have moved but this music moves the soul of subcontinent.

I feel the new generation of millennials are more appreciative of this music which cuts through so many boundaries.
